  <entry>
    <title>【PC】樱之杜†净梦者2</title>
    <link href="https://yinghu.netlify.app/posts/7b8fd852.html"/>
    <id>https://yinghu.netlify.app/posts/7b8fd852.html</id>
    <published>2024-05-10T01:22:05.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-05-10T01:40:08.838Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>· 短暂的平静<br>打倒宿敌·小丑（ジョーカー）后、由他招之的大量恶灵（ボダッハ）已从桜之杜中统统消失。<br>桜之杜又恢复了平静的日常。<br>但这份平静、也不过是昙花一现。<br>· 新的恶梦来临<br>恶梦再度袭来。<br>那里是、吞噬人类的怪物、已死的杀人魔横行的、赤色世界。<br>那的死、会导致在现实中死亡。<br>——为守护小镇。乃至守护深爱之人。<br>桜之杜的净梦者们（サクラノモリ ・ ドリーマーズ）再度、投身于战斗之中。<br>· 有まどか相伴的日常<br>而与まどか所度过的日常。<br>只会是一场甜美的噩梦吗？<br>亦或······。<br>无论是恶梦、还是与你共度的南柯之梦——<br>都已不在是一场梦。</p><p><img src="https://r2.touchgal.net/2023/12/62f6bff0e120231221010315-1024x576.jpg">可怕</img></p><hr><a class="btn-beautify " href="http://111.173.104.54:5244/d/%E6%A2%93%E6%BE%AA%E5%A6%99%E5%A6%99%E5%B1%8B%EF%BC%88zi0.cc%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90(gal%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90)/%60%E3%80%90%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E3%80%91/%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96galgame%E4%BC%9A%E7%A4%BE%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86/%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96%E4%BC%9A%E7%A4%BE%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%20part14/MOONSTONE/MOONSTONE/%5B190315%5D%5BMOONSTONE%5D%20%E6%A8%B1%E4%B9%8B%E6%9D%9C%E2%80%A0%E5%87%80%E6%A2%A6%E8%80%852%20steam%E7%89%88%20(files).rar"   title="点击下载"><i class="red larger"></i><span>点击下载</span></a>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
